songs.title: Cameron Dallas Is My Boyfriend
songs.lyrics:
[Verse]
Oh, his eyes, how I love his eyes
Oh, his smile, how I want his smile
His hair, so Voluptuous
I just want him now

[Chorus]
'Cause he's Cameron Dallas, he's my boyfriend
Oh, I love him so
And you can't have him 'cause he's all my own
It's Cameron Dallas
Cameron Dallas, he's my boyfriend
Oh, I love him so
Cameron Dallas, he's my boyfriend
And I love him so, Cameron Dallas
